                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9820" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1483</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1085 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“财”智赋能，光模块创新领航——联特科技创新进阶之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Financial” wisdom empowered, optical module innovation to lead the way--Unitech&#39;s road to innovation and advancement</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈汉芳，陈卫东，龚申，冯竣凯，金诗语</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉联特科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务成本；成本管控；科技创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">financial costs; cost control; science and technology innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在5G网络建设加速、数据中心规模扩张，以及生成式 AI 技术驱动全球算力需求爆发的多重因素作用下，光通信行业迎来发展浪潮，光模块市场随之进入高速增长期。作为专注于光通信收发模块研发、生产与销售的联特科技，在把握市场机遇的同时，亟需通过强化竞争力实现可持续发展。本文以财务成本管控体系建设为核心，深入剖析科技型企业在“技术研发创新”与“产品质量管控体系建设”的双重需求下，精细化财务管控策略的实施路径与成效，着重探讨企业如何通过“阶段性全面成本管控—研发费用集中管控—全流程质量成本管控”的递进路径，为光模块关键技术攻坚提供支撑，并助力研发创新可持续推进。本案例旨在深化财务成本管控理论认知，以鲜活实践案例揭示成本管控在企业科技创新进程中驱动资源整合、助力技术迭代的关键作用机制。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Driven by multiple factors such as the accelerated construction of 5G networks, the expansion of data center scales, and the explosive growth of global computing power demand driven by generative AI technologies, the optical communication industry has ushered in a wave of development, and the optical module market has accordingly entered a period of rapid growth. As Unitech, a company specializing in the research and development (R&amp;D), production, and sales of optical communication transceiver modules, it urgently needs to enhance its competitiveness to achieve sustainable development while seizing market opportunities. Focusing on the construction of a financial cost control system as its core, this paper conducts an in-depth analysis of the implementation paths and effects of refined financial cost control strategies for technology-based enterprises under the dual demands of &quot;technological R&amp;D innovation&quot; and &quot;construction of product quality control systems&quot;. It emphasizes exploring how enterprises can provide support for key technological breakthroughs in optical modules and facilitate the sustainable advancement of R&amp;D innovation through the progressive path of &quot;phased comprehensive cost control - centralized R&amp;D expense control - full-process cost control&quot;. This case aims to deepen the theoretical understanding of financial cost control and reveal the key mechanism by which cost control drives resource integration and facilitates technological iteration in the process of enterprise technological innovation through vivid practical cases.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计》、《成本管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">产品成本；产品生命周期成本管理；财务成本管理；质量成本管理；分布式创新；企业创新驱动</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
